column2: select Track.GenreId as &&&, Genre.GenreId as ID, Genre.Name as &&&, Track.MediaTypeId as &&&, MediaType.MediaTypeId as &&&, MediaType.Name as &&&   From chinook.Track Inner Join chinook.genre on Track.GenreId = Genre.GenreId Inner Join chinook.MediaType on Track.MediaTypeId = MediaType.MediaTypeId Group by MediaTypeId
